{"word":"G4226 - ποῦ - poû - poo - Where","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ποῦ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">poû</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">poo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Where</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"எங்கே - எதிர்மறை வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"where? in what place?"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Genitive case of <b>&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C2;</b> <b>pos</b>, an interrogitive pronoun, (<i>what</i>) otherwise obsolete (perhaps the same as <a href=\"#/G4225 - πού - poú - poo/4225\">G4225</a> used with the rising slide of inquiry); as adverb of place; <i>at</i> (by implication <i>to</i>) <i>what</i> locality: - where, whither.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}